R/_disable_autoload.R






In the documentation for loadSupport(), you’ll find an option to remove the R/ directory sourcing by placing a file named _disable_autoload.R in your R/ directory (this is also one of the behaviors of the golem framework, which we will cover in the following chapters).
It’s perfectly fine to adopt this behavior–this chapter demonstrates a way to remove the loadSupport warning without having to add this file.
